Dubai, United Arab Emirates
Egypt PR & Media Specialist
Posted: 5 days, 7 hours ago
My client is looking for an Egypt-based freelance journalist or PR/media outreach specialist that has deep contacts in the Egyptian media/new media/social media world.
We would be looking for your help to contact existing Egyptian media particularly interested in startups and youth employment issues.
We would like to have you pitch a few stories or set-up interviews during an upcoming trip.
Please get in touch only if you have existing relationships in Egypt and have already done media outreach.
Please tell us what outlets or publications you have contacts with.
Thanks.
